dct_title_s: New Brunswick and Highland Park, New Jersey 1948
dct_description_sm: Map depicts the boroughs of New Brunswick and Highland Park with the Raritan River running between them. Key highlights points of interest including schools, colleges, hospitals, public housing, libraries and parks. Original map from 1932 with revisions in 1947 and 1948.
